{"tid":1159103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隻網絡紅貓 Grumpy Cat 過咗身 ...","createTime":"2019-05-17T12:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T12:20:05.000Z","uid":252523,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1015c43b76b55fbb5ba21039e5a859b1fefb6f86","tid":1159103,"uid":252523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"Grumpy Cat （中譯： 不爽貓），原本係一隻叫做Tardar Sauce嘅雌貓。因為患有骨軟骨發育不全症，所以佢個樣望落去成日都係暴躁易怒咁款。<br />\n<br />\n佢主人既哥哥有次將不爽貓既照片放上去外國大型討論區Reddit之後，引起國際網民既討論，成為話題，令佢一夜成名。佢喺Facebook既專頁差唔多有成700萬fans，仲試過登上華爾街日報頭版，之後亦有喺音樂MV以及電影亮相。<br />\n<br />\n令人傷心既係呢隻網絡紅貓因為感染同併發症，於5月14日安祥辭世，享年7歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHkTLqE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHkTLqE.png&h=2b4936a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLZpR5K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLZpR5K.png&h=b46d3ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貓貓一路好走<br />\n喺彩虹另一邊要開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e073501420272365340976c6f1ecbe3c93dd306","tid":1159103,"uid":252523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YM2F9VZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYM2F9VZ.png&h=cc787cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XfenF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XfenF.png&h=dbf50786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMRzuV1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMRzuV1.png&h=5252739f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEFo7HH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEFo7HH.png&h=9343f765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GgnyLun.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://